<%= form_for @project do |f| %>
Title
<%= f.text_field :title,  placeholder: 'title', required: true %>
Subtitle
<%= f.text_field :subtitle,  placeholder: 'subtitle', required: true %>
Description
<%= f.text_field :description,  placeholder: 'description', required: true %>
Basic info
What field does your project fall under?
<%= f.select(:field, @fields) %>
What kind of person are you looking for? Maximum 5



  <input type="text" name="positions[]" />
